        "subject": "LU-276 tests: avoid the impact of config reprocessing",
        "message": "LU-276 tests: avoid the impact of config reprocessing\n\nin test_18 of ost-pools, the creation performance of with-pool and\nwith-missing-pool is measured just after the operations of pool,\nwhich will cause the config llog to be reprocessed in clients and\nservers and could impact the performance of file creation.\n\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I00c1a443c20713e6675e2a7b93d2d6c83576839e\n"
      },
